      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still firm and the 'new car' scent preserved. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear on any components. This is a collector-quality example that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
