      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The vehicle has undergone proactive maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry for balanced turn-in, while the braking system remains sharp with consistent pedal feel. This is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated era, showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with a well-maintained driver's car.",
